===========================================================================
SUMMARY: ALL CLAIMS VERIFIED
===========================================================================

  Claim 1: n=2 and n=4 are the only non-trivial dimensions
           where R_n has pure power-of-two denominator.
           PROVEN by m! analysis (m>=3 has odd prime factor).

  Claim 2: R_3 = pi/6 separates in 8/8 sphere-volume equations.
           R_2 = pi/4 separates in 2/2 cross-section equations.
           All verified as EXACT Fraction identities.

  Claim 3: R_4 = pi^2/32 separates in the 4D one-loop integral
           BEFORE Fourier normalization.
           I_n = 32*R_4 * Gamma(n-2)/(Gamma(n)*M^{2n-4})
           Verified: 32*R_4 = pi^2 (EXACT).

  Claim 4: Instanton action S = 8*pi^2/g^2 = 256*R_4/g^2
           Chern class 1/(8*pi^2) = 1/(256*R_4)
           Both EXACT Fraction identities.

  Q335 native: R_2 = p(pi)>>2, R_4 = p(pi^2)>>5
  Both are bit-shifts on Q335 numerators (no odd denominators).

